{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I spent the best part of last year"},{"time":5000,"text":"working on a documentary"},{"time":8000,"text":"about my own happiness --"},{"time":10000,"text":"trying to see"},{"time":12000,"text":"if I can actually train my mind"},{"time":14000,"text":"in a particular way,"},{"time":17000,"text":"like I can train my body,"},{"time":19000,"text":"so I can end up with an improved feeling"},{"time":22000,"text":"of overall well-being."},{"time":25000,"text":"Then this January,"},{"time":27000,"text":"my mother died,"},{"time":29000,"text":"and pursuing a film like that"},{"time":32000,"text":"just seemed the last thing that was interesting to me."},{"time":36000,"text":"So in a very typical, silly designer fashion,"},{"time":40000,"text":"after years worth of work,"},{"time":43000,"text":"pretty much all I have to show for it are the titles for the film."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":53000,"text":"They were still done"},{"time":55000,"text":"when I was on sabbatical with my company in Indonesia."},{"time":57000,"text":"We can see the first part here was designed here by pigs."},{"time":60000,"text":"It was a little bit too funky,"},{"time":62000,"text":"and we wanted a more feminine point of view"},{"time":65000,"text":"and employed a duck"},{"time":67000,"text":"who did it in a much more fitting way --"},{"time":69000,"text":"fashion."},{"time":72000,"text":"My studio in Bali"},{"time":74000,"text":"was only 10 minutes away from a monkey forest,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and monkeys, of course,"},{"time":79000,"text":"are supposed to be the happiest of all animals."},{"time":81000,"text":"So we trained them to be able to do three separate words,"},{"time":84000,"text":"to lay out them properly."},{"time":86000,"text":"You can see,"},{"time":88000,"text":"there still is a little bit of a legibility problem there."},{"time":91000,"text":"The serif is not really in place."},{"time":93000,"text":"So of course, what you don't do properly yourself"},{"time":96000,"text":"is never deemed done really."},{"time":98000,"text":"So this is us climbing onto the trees"},{"time":101000,"text":"and putting it up over the Sayan Valley"},{"time":104000,"text":"in Indonesia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"In that year, what I did do a lot"},{"time":110000,"text":"was look at all sorts of surveys,"},{"time":112000,"text":"looking at a lot of data on this subject."},{"time":115000,"text":"And it turns out"},{"time":117000,"text":"that men and women"},{"time":120000,"text":"report very, very similar levels of happiness."},{"time":123000,"text":"This is a very quick overview"},{"time":125000,"text":"of all the studies that I looked at."},{"time":127000,"text":"That climate plays no role."},{"time":129000,"text":"That if you live in the best climate,"},{"time":131000,"text":"in San Diego in the United States,"},{"time":133000,"text":"or in the shittiest climate, in Buffalo, New York,"},{"time":136000,"text":"you are going to be just as happy"},{"time":138000,"text":"in either place."},{"time":140000,"text":"If you make more than 50,000 bucks a year in the U.S.,"},{"time":144000,"text":"any salary increase you're going to experience"},{"time":147000,"text":"will have only a tiny, tiny influence"},{"time":150000,"text":"on your overall well-being."},{"time":152000,"text":"Black people are just as happy as white people are."},{"time":155000,"text":"If you're old or young"},{"time":157000,"text":"it doesn't really make a difference."},{"time":159000,"text":"If you're ugly or if you're really, really good-looking"},{"time":162000,"text":"it makes no difference whatsoever."},{"time":164000,"text":"You will adapt to it and get used to it."},{"time":166000,"text":"If you have manageable health problems"},{"time":169000,"text":"it doesn't really matter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":171000,"text":"Now this does matter."},{"time":173000,"text":"So now the woman on the right"},{"time":175000,"text":"is actually much happier than the guy on the left --"},{"time":178000,"text":"meaning that, if you have a lot of friends,"},{"time":181000,"text":"and you have meaningful friendships,"},{"time":184000,"text":"that does make a lot of difference."},{"time":186000,"text":"As well as being married -- you are likely to be much happier"},{"time":189000,"text":"than if you are single."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191000,"text":"A fellow TED speaker, Jonathan Haidt,"},{"time":193000,"text":"came up with this beautiful little analogy"},{"time":196000,"text":"between the conscious and the unconscious mind."},{"time":200000,"text":"He says that the conscious mind is this tiny rider"},{"time":203000,"text":"on this giant elephant, the unconscious."},{"time":206000,"text":"And the rider thinks"},{"time":208000,"text":"that he can tell the elephant what to do,"},{"time":211000,"text":"but the elephant really has his own ideas."},{"time":214000,"text":"If I look at my own life,"},{"time":216000,"text":"I'm born in 1962 in Austria."},{"time":219000,"text":"If I would have been born a hundred years earlier,"},{"time":222000,"text":"the big decisions in my life would have been made for me --"},{"time":225000,"text":"meaning I would have stayed in the town that I was born in;"},{"time":229000,"text":"I would have very much likely"},{"time":231000,"text":"entered the same profession that my dad did;"},{"time":233000,"text":"and I would have very much likely married a woman"},{"time":236000,"text":"that my mom had selected."},{"time":240000,"text":"I, of course, and all of us,"},{"time":243000,"text":"are very much in charge"},{"time":245000,"text":"of these big decisions in our lives."},{"time":248000,"text":"We live where we want to be --"},{"time":250000,"text":"at least in the West."},{"time":252000,"text":"We become what we really are interested in."},{"time":254000,"text":"We choose our own profession,"},{"time":256000,"text":"and we choose our own partners."},{"time":258000,"text":"And so it's quite surprising"},{"time":261000,"text":"that many of us"},{"time":263000,"text":"let our unconscious influence those decisions"},{"time":266000,"text":"in ways that we are not quite aware of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"If you look at the statistics"},{"time":272000,"text":"and you see that the guy called George,"},{"time":275000,"text":"when he decides on where he wants to live --"},{"time":278000,"text":"is it Florida or North Dakota? --"},{"time":281000,"text":"he goes and lives in Georgia."},{"time":283000,"text":"And if you look at a guy called Dennis,"},{"time":285000,"text":"when he decides what to become --"},{"time":287000,"text":"is it a lawyer, or does he want to become a doctor"},{"time":290000,"text":"or a teacher? --"},{"time":292000,"text":"best chance is that he wants to become a dentist."},{"time":295000,"text":"And if Paula decides"},{"time":297000,"text":"should she marry Joe or Jack,"},{"time":299000,"text":"somehow Paul sounds the most interesting."},{"time":303000,"text":"And so even if we make"},{"time":305000,"text":"those very important decisions"},{"time":307000,"text":"for very silly reasons,"},{"time":309000,"text":"it remains statistically true"},{"time":311000,"text":"that there are more Georges living in Georgia"},{"time":313000,"text":"and there are more Dennises becoming dentists"},{"time":316000,"text":"and there are more Paulas who are married to Paul"},{"time":319000,"text":"than statistically viable."},{"time":321000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":323000,"text":"Now I, of course, thought,"},{"time":326000,"text":"\"Well this is American data,\""},{"time":328000,"text":"and I thought, \"Well, those silly Americans."},{"time":332000,"text":"They get influenced by things"},{"time":335000,"text":"that they're not aware of."},{"time":338000,"text":"This is just completely ridiculous.\""},{"time":341000,"text":"Then, of course, I looked at my mom and my dad --"},{"time":344000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":346000,"text":"Karolina and Karl,"},{"time":348000,"text":"and grandmom and granddad,"},{"time":351000,"text":"Josefine and Josef."},{"time":353000,"text":"So I am looking still for a Stephanie."},{"time":355000,"text":"I'll figure something out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":359000,"text":"If I make this whole thing a little bit more personal"},{"time":361000,"text":"and see what makes me happy as a designer,"},{"time":364000,"text":"the easiest answer, of course,"},{"time":366000,"text":"is do more of the stuff that I like to do"},{"time":369000,"text":"and much less of the stuff that I don't like to do --"},{"time":371000,"text":"for which it would be helpful"},{"time":374000,"text":"to know what it is that I actually do like to do."},{"time":377000,"text":"I'm a big list maker,"},{"time":379000,"text":"so I came up with a list."},{"time":381000,"text":"One of them is to think without pressure."},{"time":384000,"text":"This is a project we're working on right now"},{"time":386000,"text":"with a very healthy deadline."},{"time":388000,"text":"It's a book on culture,"},{"time":390000,"text":"and, as you can see,"},{"time":392000,"text":"culture is rapidly drifting around."},{"time":395000,"text":"Doing things like I'm doing right now --"},{"time":397000,"text":"traveling to Cannes."},{"time":399000,"text":"The example I have here"},{"time":401000,"text":"is a chair that came out of the year in Bali --"},{"time":404000,"text":"clearly influenced by local manufacturing and culture,"},{"time":408000,"text":"not being stuck behind"},{"time":410000,"text":"a single computer screen all day long"},{"time":413000,"text":"and be here and there."},{"time":415000,"text":"Quite consciously, design projects"},{"time":417000,"text":"that need an incredible amount of various techniques,"},{"time":420000,"text":"just basically to fight"},{"time":422000,"text":"straightforward adaptation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":425000,"text":"Being close to the content --"},{"time":427000,"text":"that's the content really is close to my heart."},{"time":430000,"text":"This is a bus, or vehicle,"},{"time":432000,"text":"for a charity, for an NGO"},{"time":434000,"text":"that wants to double the education budget in the United States --"},{"time":438000,"text":"carefully designed,"},{"time":440000,"text":"so, by two inches, it still clears highway overpasses."},{"time":447000,"text":"Having end results -- things that come back from the printer well,"},{"time":451000,"text":"like this little business card for an animation company"},{"time":453000,"text":"called Sideshow"},{"time":455000,"text":"on lenticular foils."},{"time":458000,"text":"Working on projects"},{"time":460000,"text":"that actually have visible impacts,"},{"time":462000,"text":"like a book for a deceased German artist"},{"time":467000,"text":"whose widow came to us"},{"time":470000,"text":"with the requirement to make her late husband famous."},{"time":474000,"text":"It just came out six months ago,"},{"time":476000,"text":"and it's getting unbelievable traction right now in Germany."},{"time":480000,"text":"And I think that his widow"},{"time":482000,"text":"is going to be very successful on her quest."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486000,"text":"And lately, to be involved in projects"},{"time":489000,"text":"where I know about 50 percent of the project"},{"time":491000,"text":"technique-wise"},{"time":493000,"text":"and the other 50 percent would be new."},{"time":495000,"text":"So in this case,"},{"time":497000,"text":"it's an outside projection for Singapore"},{"time":499000,"text":"on these giant Times Square-like screens."},{"time":502000,"text":"And I of course knew stuff, as a designer,"},{"time":505000,"text":"about typography,"},{"time":507000,"text":"even though we worked with those animals not so successfully."},{"time":510000,"text":"But I didn't quite know"},{"time":512000,"text":"all that much about movement or film."},{"time":515000,"text":"And from that point of view we turned it into a lovely project."},{"time":518000,"text":"But also because the content was very close."},{"time":521000,"text":"In this case, \"Keeping a Diary"},{"time":523000,"text":"Supports Personal Development\" --"},{"time":525000,"text":"I've been keeping a diary since I was 12."},{"time":528000,"text":"And I've found that it influenced my life and work"},{"time":532000,"text":"in a very intriguing way."},{"time":535000,"text":"In this case also because"},{"time":537000,"text":"it's part of one of the many sentiments"},{"time":540000,"text":"that we build the whole series on --"},{"time":544000,"text":"that all the sentiments originally had come out of the diary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}